{"tid":794103,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《全民造星》爆內訌 導師劉美君扯火轟評判亂嚟","createTime":"2018-08-26T02:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T13:51:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbd47f1b1a967262ebe5f685bd236fb05486bd8","tid":794103,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:42:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180826/20484675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F20484675&d=Ffc2IM8%2B%2BBCfU1b%2BtQePjjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2181ceb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F20484675&h=20dfc932\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180826/20484675</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月26日 <br />\n<br />\n《全民造星》爆內訌<br />\n導師劉美君扯火轟評判亂嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180826/large/26ec1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180826%2Flarge%2F26ec1p1.jpg&h=2608c3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身為導師的劉美君對參賽者甚為上心，對於廢評㷫到爆。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTV選秀真人騷《Good Night Show全民造星》自7月中播出後，是非不絕。上周播出的28、29集請來蕭定一、張建聲及吳漢邦等擔任星級評判，卻被網友插爆，導師劉美君更扯火怒轟評判亂嚟，更從後台衝出台前與評判對質，監製「花姐」黃慧君亦直說：「火都嚟埋呀！」<br />\n<br />\n選秀真人騷《全民造星》已播至30集，最近播出的幾集請來其中一個合作夥伴HMV數碼中國集團的五位代表包括主席蕭定一、歌手鄧健泓、導演吳漢邦、演員張建聲及趙永洪擔任星級評判，但卻成為眾矢之的。當參賽者表演完後，張建聲竟問：「你個頭（髮型）搞乜？」蕭定一再下一城問：「你覺唔覺得Oscar呢個名比較普通？會唔會好容易同人撞名？」而導演吳漢邦亦寸爆︰「啲帽點解要掟？」<br />\n<br />\n大堆廢評成功點燃多位導師，卓韻芝在後台狂寸他們hea，郭偉亮亦說他們只懂抨擊名字、髮型，監製花姐亦不禁鬧爆：「可唔可以講啲有意義嘅嘢&hellip;&hellip;火都嚟埋呀！」反應最激烈的就是劉美君，更㷫到在後台爆seed：「頂你個肺！」再衝出舞台與評判對質。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180826/large/26ec1p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180826%2Flarge%2F26ec1p4.jpg&h=6ee8cda6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評判蕭定一（左）與張建聲的評語被網民鬧爆評語太廢。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180826/large/26ec1p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180826%2Flarge%2F26ec1p5.jpg&h=a242cd38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評判吳漢邦問參賽者：「啲帽點解要掟？」被卓韻芝寸太hea。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心想幫班細路<br />\n<br />\n劉美君昨日接受《蘋果》訪問，她說：「我忍無可忍決定講清楚，我都戥ViuTV唔抵，因為有人喺網絡留言，認為有設計情節。」她坦言：「我呢個人鍾意伸張正義，做呢個節目係想幫呢班有心喺呢個圈發展嘅細路，有人唔認真批評，我好勞氣。」<br />\n<br />\n花姐亦否認是設計情節︰「如果我要咁設計情節，一定俾老細斬死！」問是否有贊助才可以出鏡？她解釋︰「唔係，只係搵幾間公司去support我哋，佢哋喺參賽者中搵有潛質嘅人。」<br />\n<br />\n被評名字太普通的涂心業（Oscar）回應︰「唔係好愕然，但預期comment係同表演有關。」另一參賽者姜濤表示：「我喺後台聽都有啲奇怪，唔係好理解，好似搞唔清重點。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180826/large/c0101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180826%2Flarge%2Fc0101a.gif&h=7768f4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n監製花姐、卓韻芝、郭偉亮、杜汶澤都寸評判不知所云。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180826/large/26ec1p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180826%2Flarge%2F26ec1p3.jpg&h=642dc4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參賽者姜濤在後台聽到評語亦覺得奇怪。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180826/large/26ec1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180826%2Flarge%2F26ec1p2.jpg&h=a887c421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOscar（右二）在節目中用心表演，卻被蕭定一批評名字太普通。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿澤爆粗撐學員<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤亦於fb留言︰「Oscar，你個名太普通喇！你以後就叫9527啦！」阿澤更不忿爆粗：「踩人邊個唔識吖？做人冇X用好小事，黑X心兼無品嗰吓大件事。」<br />\n<br />\n據當晚現場錄影人士透露，參賽者當中有三、四位參賽者叫Oscar，有些更為此改名，所以蕭定一才有此一問，其實錄影時他也有給予意見，但偏偏節目卻大刀一剪，變成「斷章取義」。成為箭靶的蕭定一就封嘴說︰「冇回應。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪︰皓鶱、霍淇、陳杰  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【另類贈言】星級評判揀蟀入娛圈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【另類贈言】星級評判揀蟀入娛圈<br />\n<br />\n【是非不斷】參賽者疑fb買票"},{"pid":"fdd4045943a417c3d03759c34f1f459cfa889346","tid":794103,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾評判</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c4b51428a2da1ae8e6859caed743491984d7bcaa","tid":794103,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"skr🤙🤙🤙🤙"},{"pid":"8264b0a84b8a559c5646a4ce855863fef9872434","tid":794103,"uid":49391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T08:53:41.000Z","msg":"好心就搵杜汶澤做評判啦"},{"pid":"aff12391777249cdbca1af0b4e1484e05cd647fa","tid":794103,"uid":36441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"搵啲評判都幾九唔搭八架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c624787039d22853543793a9d703d09747764ce0","tid":794103,"uid":96,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"aff12391777249cdbca1af0b4e1484e05cd647fa","tid":794103,"uid":36441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"搵啲評判都幾九唔搭八架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"冇睇過但班星級評判自己都紅唔起 有咩資格評人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ebc8989b926f74f3e98a00ae96a991e6f842be","tid":794103,"uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"c624787039d22853543793a9d703d09747764ce0","tid":794103,"uid":96,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"aff12391777249cdbca1af0b4e1484e05cd647fa","tid":794103,"uid":36441,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"搵啲評判都幾九唔搭八架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad